headline.main: DESERT R.A.F. RAKES AXIS UNIT ON PARADE; Rows of Troops Gunned in Raid on Garrison Below Tripoli

lead_paragraph: CAIRO, Egypt, Nov. 8 -- Thursday was parade day for a majority of the garrison at the Axis post and airdrome of Mallaha, which is south of Tripoli, Libya. Rows of soldiers stood at attention as rain whipped across barrack buildings.
abstract: RAF machine-guns Axis unit on parade, Mallaha airdrome, Libya; other Libya points bombed; 3 Axis planes downed over Malta
